name: Cursed (itch) (orlev)
description:
This is my first ever completed (sorta) game, and therefore, my first jam. It's not polished, but I think it has potential..

I had very little time to work on this, and have been up until the morning just trying to get all of this done.. So I do hope it at least brings a smile to your face. 

p.s., 4 minutes before the jam closed, I see there's a bug where the level doesn't change... oh well.. It was amazing let me tell you...

jk.
